extended to 50-41 with 7:50 remaining. Six minutes later, Germany
closed to 54-55 with a 13-5 run with 1:40 left.
</P>
<P>
Slovakia took over again and clinched the must-win game for the
quarterfinals.
</P>
<P>
Germany will play in the classification matches with other
three disqualifiers in the second run with two from each group.
