(G-8) and European Union (EU) states.
</P>
<P>
Indonesia, Columbia, and South Africa -- past, present, and future
chairs of the movement - recently met British Foreign Minister Robin
Cook to discuss debt relief for indebted nations, Business Day paper
reported Monday.
